@FingerPrintVerfication_HostAddress = http://localhost:8080

### FingerPrint Verification API Tests

### 1. Add Person with 5 Fingerprints
POST {{FingerPrintVerfication_HostAddress}}/api/person
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "John Doe",
  "companyName": "Tech Corp",
  "jobTitle": "Software Engineer",
  "fingerPrints": [
    "/uploads/fingerprints/john_thumb_left.jpg",
    "/uploads/fingerprints/john_index_left.jpg", 
    "/uploads/fingerprints/john_middle_left.jpg",
    "/uploads/fingerprints/john_ring_left.jpg",
    "/uploads/fingerprints/john_pinky_left.jpg"
  ]
}

### 2. Add Another Person
POST {{FingerPrintVerfication_HostAddress}}/api/person
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Jane Smith",
  "companyName": "Security Inc",
  "jobTitle": "Security Analyst",
  "fingerPrints": [
    "/uploads/fingerprints/jane_thumb_left.jpg",
    "/uploads/fingerprints/jane_index_left.jpg",
