}

### 3. Verify Person by Fingerprint Path
GET {{FingerPrintVerfication_HostAddress}}/api/person/verify?fingerprintPath=/uploads/fingerprints/john_thumb_left.jpg

### 4. Verify Person with Non-existent Fingerprint
GET {{FingerPrintVerfication_HostAddress}}/api/person/verify?fingerprintPath=/uploads/fingerprints/nonexistent.jpg

### 5. Get All Persons (Paginated)
GET {{FingerPrintVerfication_HostAddress}}/api/person?page=1&pageSize=10

### 6. Get Person by ID
GET {{FingerPrintVerfication_HostAddress}}/api/person/1

### 7. Get Audit Logs
GET {{FingerPrintVerfication_HostAddress}}/api/person/audit-logs?page=1&pageSize=10

### 8. Get Audit Logs - Filter by Successful Operations
GET {{FingerPrintVerfication_HostAddress}}/api/person/audit-logs?page=1&pageSize=10&isSuccessful=true

### 9. Get Audit Logs - Filter by Verification Operations
GET {{FingerPrintVerfication_HostAddress}}/api/person/audit-logs?page=1&pageSize=10&auditType=2

### 10. Get Audit Logs - Filter by User ID
GET {{FingerPrintVerfication_HostAddress}}/api/person/audit-logs?page=1&pageSize=10&userId=1

### 11. Delete Person
DELETE {{FingerPrintVerfication_HostAddress}}/api/person/1

